@startuml
[*] --> Idle

Idle --> Recruitment: recruit employee
Recruitment --> AddingEmployee: admin adds employee
AddingEmployee --> DatabaseUpdate: update database with new employee
DatabaseUpdate --> AdminApproval: awaiting admin approval
AdminApproval --> Approved: approved by admin
AdminApproval --> Rejected: rejected by admin

Idle --> DealerManagement: manage dealer information
DealerManagement --> AddingDealer: add dealer
DealerManagement --> ChangingDealer: change dealer info

Idle --> ProductLoading: load products
ProductLoading --> AwaitingAdminApproval: awaiting admin approval for employee update
AwaitingAdminApproval --> ApprovedUpdate: approved by admin, update database
AwaitingAdminApproval --> RejectedUpdate: rejected by admin

Idle --> AlertsManagement: receive SMS alerts for fires
AlertsManagement --> FireDetected: fire detected by camera

Idle --> CCTVFootageManagement: delete old or unnecessary footage
CCTVFootageManagement --> DeletingOldFootage: delete old footage

Idle --> PriceAdjustment: adjust retail prices based on market demand
PriceAdjustment --> AdjustedPrices: new prices set

Idle --> ProfitLossData: view profit or loss data for specific time periods
ProfitLossData --> DataViewed: data viewed

Idle --> OrdersPlacement: place orders from dealers
OrdersPlacement --> OrderPlaced: order placed successfully

Idle --> CustomerSuggestions: review customer suggestions to improve service quality
CustomerSuggestions --> SuggestionReviewed: suggestion reviewed

@enduml
